
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Huy Hoang Bio</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif}

body{
height:100vh;
background:#000814;
color:white;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
overflow:hidden;
}

/* star background */
body::before{
content:"";
position:fixed;
width:200%;
height:200%;
background:url("https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png");
animation:stars 120s linear infinite;
opacity:.5;
}

@keyframes stars{
from{transform:translateY(0)}
to{transform:translateY(-1000px)}
}

.container{display:flex;gap:30px;z-index:2;}

.card,.panel{
background:#041020;
padding:35px;
border-radius:20px;
width:420px;
box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(0,255,255,.15);
}

.profile{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-bottom:20px;}

.avatar{
width:110px;
height:110px;
border-radius:50%;
background-image:url("avatar.png");
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
border:3px solid #00ffff;
animation:avatarGlow 3s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes avatarGlow{
0%{box-shadow:0 0 10px #00ffff;transform:scale(1)}
100%{box-shadow:0 0 35px #00ffff;transform:scale(1.05)}
}

.name{font-size:26px;font-weight:600;color:#00ffff;}
.role{font-size:14px;opacity:.7;}
.tags{margin-top:15px;font-size:14px;opacity:.8;}

.btns{margin-top:20px;display:flex;gap:15px;}

.btn{
flex:1;
padding:12px;
border-radius:10px;
background:transparent;
border:1px solid #00ffff;
color:#00ffff;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{background:#00ffff;color:black;}

.title{color:#00ffff;margin-bottom:15px;font-weight:600;font-size:20px;}
.message{line-height:1.8;font-size:15px;opacity:.9;}

footer{text-align:center;margin-top:20px;font-size:12px;opacity:.6;}

.anime{
position:fixed;
bottom:0;
left:-200px;
width:160px;
animation:run 15s linear infinite;
z-index:1;
}

@keyframes run{
0%{left:-200px}
100%{left:110%}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<audio id="music" autoplay loop>
<source src="music.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<img class="anime" src="https://media.tenor.com/7D7I6dKQJb4AAAAi/anime-run.gif">

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<div class="profile">
<div class="avatar"></div>
<div>
<div class="name">Huy Hoang</div>
<div class="role">Developer • Web • Anime Lover</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="tags">
📍 Viet Nam<br>
💻 Coding • Design • Bio Web
</div>

<div class="btns">
<button class="btn" onclick="toggleMusic()">🎵 Bật / Tắt Nhạc</button>
<button class="btn">📩 Liên hệ</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="panel">
<div class="title">Chúc mừng 8/3 💐</div>

<div class="message">
Chúc tất cả các bạn nữ một ngày <b>Quốc tế Phụ nữ 8/3</b> thật vui vẻ ❤️ <br><br>
Luôn xinh đẹp, hạnh phúc, học tập tốt và gặp nhiều may mắn trong cuộc sống ✨ <br><br>
Cảm ơn vì đã làm thế giới này trở nên tuyệt vời hơn 🌸
</div>

<footer>© 2026 Huy Hoang</footer>

</div>

</div>

<script>
const music=document.getElementById("music")
function toggleMusic(){
if(music.paused){music.play()}else{music.pause()}
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
